{"tid":519945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國總統馬克龍宣布計劃立法阻止虛假新聞","createTime":"2018-01-05T01:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T01:37:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19f54653b14dcb09c450307dfafa4ee7a5b8b0fd","tid":519945,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:37:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1373232-20180104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1373232-20180104.htm&d=wxO4TvblOyXzBSP4btRs8%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=b4554fb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1373232-20180104.htm&h=cd8f10bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1373232-20180104.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1373232_1_20180104124120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1373232_1_20180104124120.jpg&h=43f28b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍宣布，計劃立法阻止虛假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍向傳媒發表新年演說，表示將立法阻止虛假新聞破壞民主，法例細節將在數星期內發表，目標是加強透明度。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，屆時傳媒必須透露新聞來源，法官有權命令傳媒刪除虛假新聞，阻截用戶前往有問題的網站，以及刪除散播不實資料的社交媒體帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍補充，法國的監管機構將獲得更大權力，以便更好地監管由外國控制的電視頻道，防止散佈不利穩定的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍在去年五月，曾經猛烈抨擊兩個總部在俄羅斯的傳媒，散播誹謗謊言和欺騙性宣傳。"}]}